meta.name: Oracle Database
meta.description: Dashboard for the telegraf input plug-in for Oracle.
meta.author: InfluxData

cells.name: Sorts on Disk

queries.query: SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean("DISK_SORTS"))/10 AS "mean_DISK_SORTS" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."oracledb" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND time < :upperDashboardTime: AND service_name= :tnsname: AND "METRIC_NAME"='Disk_Sorts' GROUP BY time(:interval:) FILL(null)

queryConfig.rawText: SELECT non_negative_derivative(mean("DISK_SORTS"))/10 AS "mean_DISK_SORTS" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."oracledb" WHERE time > :dashboardTime: AND time < :upperDashboardTime: AND service_name= :tnsname: AND "METRIC_NAME"='Disk_Sorts' GROUP BY time(:interval:) FILL(null)

cells.note: To enable this graph, you will need to configure the [Telegraf Oracle Input plugin](https://github.com/snetsystems/telegraf/tree/release-1.18-snet/plugins/inputs/oracledb).

cells.name: Tablespace

queries.query: SELECT last("TS_CURR_SIZE") AS "last_TS_CURR_SIZE", last("TS_FREE_SIZE") AS "last_TS_FREE_SIZE", last("TS_USED_SIZE") AS "last_TS_USED_SIZE" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."oracledb" WHERE time > now() - 10m AND service_name= :tnsname: GROUP BY "TABLESPACE_NAME"

queryConfig.rawText: SELECT last("TS_CURR_SIZE") AS "last_TS_CURR_SIZE", last("TS_FREE_SIZE") AS "last_TS_FREE_SIZE", last("TS_USED_SIZE") AS "last_TS_USED_SIZE" FROM ":db:".":rp:"."oracledb" WHERE time > now() - 10m AND service_name= :tnsname: GROUP BY "TABLESPACE_NAME"

cells.note: To enable this graph, you will need to configure the [Telegraf Oracle Input plugin](https://github.com/snetsystems/telegraf/tree/release-1.18-snet/plugins/inputs/oracledb).
